tent/uploads/2018/02/Biker-Seed-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image lazyloaded" alt="" data-was-processed="true"><noscript><img width="600" height="490" src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Biker-Seed-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></div><div class="sep_25"></div><div class="post_ctn"><div class="post-title"><h2><a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/blockfi-seed-round-funding-announcement/" class="tiptip"> BlockFi Seed Round Funding Announcement </a></h2></div><div class="post-info">By <a href="https://blockfi.com/author/nickries/" title="Posts by Nick Ries" rel="author">Nick Ries</a> | <span class="comments-link tiptip">Comments are Closed</span></div><div class="entry"><p>**BlockFi Raises 1.55 Million from ConsenSys Ventures and SoFi to Bring Lending to the Cryptoasset Market** New York, Feb. 13th, 2018 —BlockFi, a New York-based, fintech company whose first product is a loan for cryptoasset owners,<a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/blockfi-seed-round-funding-announcement/" class="more-link">Read more</a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"></p></div></div></div></li><li class="blog_related_post brsc"><div class="post"><div class="post-attachement"><img width="600" height="490" src="./blockfi-raises-seriesa-led-by-valar-ventures.blade_files/cover-bitcoin-balance-600x490.jpg" data-lazy-src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cover-bitcoin-balance-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image lazyloaded" alt="" data-was-processed="true"><noscript><img width="600" height="490" src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cover-bitcoin-balance-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></div><div class="sep_25"></div><div class="post_ctn"><div class="post-title"><h2><a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/blockfi-loans-how-it-works/" class="tiptip"> BlockFi Loans: How It Works </a></h2></div><div class="post-info">By <a href="https://blockfi.com/author/block_admin/" title="Posts by block_admin" rel="author">block_admin</a> | <span class="comments-link tiptip">Comments are Closed</span></div><div class="entry"><p>The first step of our Top Secret Master Plan is to become the leading USD lender in the cryptoasset market. And our first product is a USD denominated loan enabling holders of Bitcoin and Ether<a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/blockfi-loans-how-it-works/" class="more-link">Read more</a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"></p></div></div></div></li><li class="blog_related_post brsc"><div class="post"><div class="post-attachement"><img width="600" height="490" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cover-loan-structure-hands-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt=""><noscript><img width="600" height="490" src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/cover-loan-structure-hands-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></div><div class="sep_25"></div><div class="post_ctn"><div class="post-title"><h2><a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/loan-structure-and-example/" class="tiptip"> Loan Structure and Example </a></h2></div><div class="post-info">By <a href="https://blockfi.com/author/block_admin/" title="Posts by block_admin" rel="author">block_admin</a> | <span class="comments-link tiptip">Comments are Closed</span></div><div class="entry"><p>BlockFi is proud to be transparent with our clients and offer a run through of how our loans work and exactly what to expect when taking out and paying for a BlockFi loan. In this<a href="https://blockfi.com/learn/loan-structure-and-example/" class="more-link">Read more</a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"></p></div></div></div></li><li class="blog_related_post brsc"><div class="post"><div class="post-attachement"><img width="600" height="490" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cover-bitcoin-vs-bank-cointelegraph-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt=""><noscript><img width="600" height="490" src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cover-bitcoin-vs-bank-cointelegraph-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></div><div class="sep_25"></div><div class="post_ctn"><div class="post-title"><h2><a href="https://blockfi.com/finance/introducing-blockfi-loans-backed-by-your-cryptoassets/" class="tiptip"> Introducing BlockFi: Loans Backed by Your Cryptoassets </a></h2></div><div class="post-info">By <a href="https://blockfi.com/author/block_admin/" title="Posts by block_admin" rel="author">block_admin</a> | <span class="comments-link tiptip">Comments are Closed</span></div><div class="entry"><p>BlockFi&nbsp;provides lending products to cryptoasset market participants. We recently raised seed funding to bring additional liquidity to the cryptoasset sector. Background For the first time, a financial asset has been created that is both natively<a href="https://blockfi.com/finance/introducing-blockfi-loans-backed-by-your-cryptoassets/" class="more-link">Read more</a></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"></p></div></div></div></li><li class="blog_related_post brsc"><div class="post"><div class="post-attachement"><img width="600" height="490" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAP///wAAACwAAAAAAQABAEACAkQBADs=" data-lazy-src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/cover-blockfi-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt=""><noscript><img width="600" height="490" src="https://blockfi.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/cover-blockfi-600x490.jpg" class="attachment-600x490 size-600x490 wp-post-image" alt="" /></noscript></div><div class="sep_25"></div><div class="post_ctn"><div class="post-ti